{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/uma-termas/","result":{"data":{"prismicProject":{"uid":"uma-termas","id":"5de4fe44-18e1-5f4e-be03-3c81e0f0edf1","data":{"project_title":{"html":"<p>Uma Termas</p>","text":"Uma Termas"},"client":{"html":"<p>Uma Termas</p>","text":"Uma Termas"},"location":{"html":"<p>Berlin, GE</p>","text":"Berlin, GE"},"team":{"html":"<p>Artur Neufeld, Dennis Mciness, George Edge</p>","text":"Artur Neufeld, Dennis Mciness, George Edge"},"year":{"html":"<p>2022</p>","text":"2022"},"categories":[{"category":{"slug":"identity","id":"ZMfWyhAAACEAPsyd"}},{"category":{"slug":"website","id":"ZMfW6RAAACMAPs1H"}}],"body1":[{"id":"text$9f3b62d1-13a3-4c40-80fd-8e27d833c0c7","slice_type":"text","primary":{"text":{"html":"<p>Identity and site design for Berlin based artist and art-director Uma Termas. The identity is essentially logoless, with the artists’ name seldom featured across the site, portfolio and stationary. All typographic content is a consistent uniform size across all treatments and the layout uses the same wide margins throughout, to create a utilitarian quality. The typeface is Helvetica Narrow used in sentence case. Artur Neufield used Web GL, the javascript 3D rendering engine to program complex ever shifting shapes drawing their colour palette from the page content to act as key transitions between different pages. </p>","text":"Identity and site design for Berlin based artist and art-director Uma Termas. The identity is essentially logoless, with the artists’ name seldom featured across the site, portfolio and stationary. All typographic content is a consistent uniform size across all treatments and the layout uses the same wide margins throughout, to create a utilitarian quality. The typeface is Helvetica Narrow used in sentence case. Artur Neufield used Web GL, the javascript 3D rendering engine to program complex ever shifting shapes drawing their colour palette from the page content to act as key transit